# MeuJudi CS installer releases are tracked; source code is tracked too.
# Older rule (`/meujudi-cs/*`) used to exclude the source, but it caused
# work to disappear from version control. Removed in favor of explicit
# ignores inside the CS folder (node_modules, dist, etc.) via the local
# .gitignore in MeuJudi-CS/.
!/meujudi-cs/release/MeuJudi-CS-Setup-v*.exe

